ship|European Championships]].\n\n==Tournament records==\n===FIFA Futsal World Cup===\n{{see also|FIFA Futsal World Cup}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n!colspan=8|[[FIFA Futsal World Cup|FIFA World Cup Record]]\n|-\n!width=125|Year\n!width=150|Round\n\n!width=35|Pld\n!width=35|W\n!width=35|D\n!width=35|L\n!width=35|GS\n!width=35|GA\n|-bgcolor=#9acdff\n|[[1989 FIFA Futsal World Championship|Netherlands 1989]]||'''4th Place'''||8||5||2||1||22||11\n|-\n|[[1992 FIFA Futsal World Championship|Hong Kong 1992]]||Second Round||6||3||0||3||17||18\n|-\n|[[1996 FIFA Futsal World Championship|Spain 1996]]||Second Round||6||2||0||4||17||22\n|-\n|[[2000 FIFA Futsal World Championship|Guatemala 2000]]||''Did not qualify''||-||-||-||-||-||-\n|-\n|[[2004 FIFA Futsal World Championship|Chinese Taipei 2004]]||''Did not qualify''||-||-||-||-||-||-\n|-\n|[[2008 FIFA Futsal World Cup|Brazil 2008]]||''Did not qualify''||-||-||-||-||-||-\n|-\n|[[2012 FIFA Futsal World Cup|Thailand 2012]]||''Did not qualify''||-||-||-||-||-||-\n|-\n|[[2016 FIFA Futsal World Cup|Colombia 2016]]||''Did not qualify''||-||-||-||-||-||-\n|-\n|[[2020 FIFA Futsal World Cup|Lithuania 2020]]||''Did not qualify''||-||-||-||-||-||-\n|-\n!'''Total'''||3/9||20||10||2||8||56||51\n|}\n\n===UEFA European Futsal Championship===\n{{see also|UEFA Futsal Championship}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n!colspan=8|[[UEFA Futsal Championship|UEFA European Futsal Championship Record]]\n|-\n!width=125|Year\n!width=150|Round\n\n!width=35|Pld\n!width=35|W\n!width=35|D\n!width=35|L\n!width=35|GS\n!width=35|GA\n|- style=\"background:#c96;\"\n|[[1996 UEFA Futsal Championship|Spain 1996]]||'''3rd Place'''||4||2||0||2||8||10\n|-\n|[[1999 UEFA Futsal Championship|Spain 1999]]||1st Round||3||0||1||2||1||7\n|-\n|[[2001 UEFA Futsal Championship|Russia 2001]]||''Did not qualify''||-||-||-||-||-||-\n|-\n|[[2003 UEFA Futsal Championship|Italy 2003]]||1st Round||3|