r.com/read?oid=111&aid=0000436045|script-title=ko:\ud55c\uc9c0\ubbfc-\ucd5c\uc2dc\uc6d0, \u7f8e \uc6f9\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8 '\ub4dc\ub77c\ub9c8\uc6d4\ub4dc' \uce74\uba54\uc624 \ucd9c\uc5f0|date=18 September 2015|website=enews24|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Revolutionary Love]]''\n| Byun Hyuk\n| [[TVN (South Korean TV channel)|tvN]]\n| \n| \n|- \n| 2019\n| ''[[My Fellow Citizens!]]''\n| Yang Jung-kook\n| [[KBS2]]\n| \n|\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[SF8]]'' ''Augmented Bean Pod''\n| Choi Min-Jun\n| [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation|MBC]]\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wowtv.co.kr/NewsCenter/News/Read?articleId=A202004030146&t=NN|script-title=ko:\ucd5c\uc2dc\uc6d0, \u2018SF8\u2019 \ud504\ub85c\uc81d\ud2b8 \u2018\uc99d\uac15 \ucf69\uae4d\uc9c0\u2019 \uc8fc\uc778\uacf5 \ucd9c\uc5f0|date=3 April 2020|website=wowtv.co.kr|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| TBA\n| ''Billion Dollar Heir''\n| Yue Xi Wang\n| TBA\n|\n| \n|-\n|}\n\n===Variety show===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\" \n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Network !! Notes !! Ref.\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''Secret Reports Super Summer''\n| Mnet\n| Cast\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=2| 2015\n| ''[[Infinite Challenge]]''\n| [[Munhwa Broadcasting Corporation|MBC]]\n| 6th Man\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mwave.me/en/news/news/view/90687/%5BRatings%3A-Sat-Sun%2C-04.4-5.15%5D-%E2%80%B2Infinity-Challenge%E2%80%B2-Names-SUJU-Choi-Siwon%2C-ZE%3AA-Kwang-Hee%2C-and-More-as-Final-Five-Candidates|title=\u2032Infinity Challenge\u2032 Names SUJU Choi Siwon, ZE:A Kwang Hee, and More as Final Five Candidates|date=6 April 2015|website=Mwave}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[We Got Married|We Are In Love]]''\n| [[Jiangsu TV]] \n| with [[Liu Wen (model)|Liu Wen]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://koreatimes.co.kr/www/news/world/2015/04/501_176483.html|title=Model pairs with singer in 'We Got Married'|website=The Korea Times|date=3 April 2015}}</ref> \n|}\n\n==Accolades==\n{{see also|List of awards and nominations received by Super Junior}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" \n|-\n